page.title: 14Hobbies and Interests
page.content: SOMETIMES I LIKE TO PLAY SQUASH IN MY SPARE TIME.I AM NOT A VERY GOOD PLAYER.I ALSO LIKE TO PLAY ON MY ATARI VIDEO GAMES.IT'S A GAME WHERE TWO PEOPLE CAN PLAY THAT'S MATHS GRAN PRIX.I KNIT CLOTHES FOR MY THREE SINDY DOLLS.I LIKE TO READ BOOKS LIKE "JACKPOT," SHIVER AND SHAKE, "TALES OF MRS. AND MANY OTHERS.I LIKE JOKE BOOKS AND I LIKE DOING PUZZLES MAINLY SEARCH A WORD.I LIKE TO PLAY ON MY GUITAR.I AM NOT A VERYGOOD PLAYER BECAUSE I'VE JUST STARTED.SOMETIMES I LIK TO GO OUT AND PLAY.I ALSO LIKE TO GO IN THE GARDEN.I HAVE A FLOWER BED OF MY OWN,I HAVE AN ARABIS CALLED ANGUS,SOME PANSIES AND SOME MORE FLOWERS AND PLANTS.THE THING I DO MOST IS WATCH TELEVISION.MY FAVOURITE PROGRAMES ARE SORRY, TOP OF THE POPS, ARTHUR C.
